{"tid":1302972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水連儂牆義士被廢老屌","createTime":"2019-07-10T06:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T06:52:12.000Z","uid":248571,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f1e04539dc67a2c7bffc68a8ee8960f0e910434b","tid":1302972,"uid":248571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"上水中心對出天橋連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n成班廢老一字排開輪住屌兩個義士<br />\n廢老A：「你唔配做中國人！唔好污染中國國土！」<br />\n廢老B：「比人打唔好搵警察啊！」<br />\n一眾鄉音大媽：「垃圾！垃圾！垃圾！」<br />\n兩個義士一言不發企定定用勝利的微笑回應 <br />\n型到想衝上去攬佢地<br />\n無聲勝有聲 雖然場面2vs10但義士唔駛反擊都贏咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上水粉嶺真係好多垃圾廢老<br />\n唔知係咪住得近大陸有同化定見大陸人咁on9自己都要不甘示弱<br />\n所以求大家7.13一定要幫手光復上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e06ef1666c4ff08f1fe4f34237faf5080a7822","tid":1302972,"uid":245033,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"好似630 gphone果種撚狗式微笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"d165ef7475be8985d973adeca564ebfc847fc90d","tid":1302972,"uid":263396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de711e4f17bc12b17338896aad73e47f4f970753","tid":1302972,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":